reviewText: Take it easy it was just a little kids book eh

This is a child's must have book! It is so fun to say to my kid I got something you will love to read. My child looked at the cover and smiled. I thought Oh Yes! My child read the whole book, then I like to go another step further and hunt down the show of it and if I can find it I buy it-this makes the reading so much better. This is a great, fun, and loved book.
